Sho - Farmer
===
title: Sho_dialogue
---
Shen: Greetings I am-
Sho: I know who you are. I have now wish to speak with you.
Shen: May I ask why?
Sho: You watered my crops with the blood of my family. They died for your war. My boy. My little boy. His mother. Are dead. Because of you. So once again, I have no wish to speak with you.
Shen: So be it.
